                    <span>I would consider this book required reading for anyone interested in ensuring their photography career is a profitable one! Focus On Profit is a sensible, easy read with a wealth of information about running a successful business. <BR>The computer software "Photobyte" that is included with it has streamlined my business more than I can say. <BR>I highly recommend this book.</span>
                  
